@startuml get_task_status
!include ../_common.puml

note over F: No lock interaction; no agent SDK call;\n<200ms event-loop hygiene (tested in Phase 1)
note over TS: status in {working, completed, failed} (C-01)

C  -> F  : 1. tools/call get_task_status({task_id})
F  -> TS : 2. read_status(task_id)
TS -> TS : 3. read tasks/<id>/status.json from filesystem
TS -> F  : 4. {status, elapsed_seconds, task_id}
F  -> C  : 5. CallToolResult { content: [...] }

@enduml
